<strong>Midnight Mallet</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/midnight_mallet.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">2H Blunt</a><BR>
Damage per second - 6.59<BR>
Damage 14 - Delay 44<BR>
Weight: 9.9 - BAR, DWF, OGR, TRL<BR>
Classes: <a href="/cleric/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/shaman/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">SHM</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/walking_sleep.shtml?spellID=669">Walking Sleep</a><BR>
Charges: 5<BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (Lore) <BR>
</font>
Obtained through the <a href="/quests/midnight_mallet.shtml?questID=16">Midnight Mallet</a> quest<BR>
<BR>
